<h3>Section 7: Proposal Requirements</h3>
<p><strong>Purpose:</strong> Tell agencies exactly what to submit so every proposal covers the same information.</p>
<p><strong>WHAT YOUR PROPOSAL MUST INCLUDE</strong></p>
<p>Please submit a proposal that includes all of the following:</p>
<ol>
<li><strong>Agency overview.</strong> Founded, team size, clients served, key specializations</li>
<li><strong>Proposed strategy.</strong> A specific, prioritized strategy based on our company background (not a generic template)</li>
<li><strong>Case studies.</strong> 1 to 2 case studies from clients in our industry or with comparable starting metrics</li>
<li><strong>Deliverables list.</strong> Exact monthly deliverables for each module, with owner assigned</li>
<li><strong>Team assignment.</strong> Names and roles of the people who will work on our account</li>
<li><strong>Pricing breakdown.</strong> Itemized by module, one-time vs. monthly, and what triggers additional billing</li>
<li><strong>Tools and technology.</strong> List of primary marketing tools used and why</li>
<li><strong>Reporting sample.</strong> 1 example of a monthly client report</li>
<li><strong>References.</strong> 2 to 3 client references available for a call</li>
</ol>
<p><strong>Format:</strong> PDF or Google Slides, maximum 25 pages
<strong>Submission:</strong> [email address or submission portal link]</p>
